<ptxt>Piston</ptxt>
<step3>
<ptxt>The pistons are made of aluminum alloy.</ptxt>
</step3>
<step3>
<ptxt>The tops of the pistons use a taper squish shape to achieve fuel combustion efficiency.</ptxt>
</step3>
<step3>
<ptxt>The piston skirt is coated with resin to reduce friction losses.</ptxt>
</step3>
<step3>
<ptxt>The groove of the top ring has been coated with anodic oxide to improve wear resistance and rust resistance.</ptxt>
